kvjson
======

kvjson is a simple command-line tool for converting JSON files to a simple
key-value format, so that JSON content can be easily processed with
standard line-based Unix text-processing tools such as grep, sed, awk.

Dependencies
============

A standard Unix-like base system with C compiler and development headers.

Build & Install
===============

./configure ~
make install

Usage
=====

e.g.

./kvjson <file.json | grep /hello/foobar | cut -d: -f2-

See also
========

https://github.com/tleino/kvxml
